BSD/Jail version 0.01
=====================

An perl interface to the FreeBSD jail() system call family.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    FreeBSD jail(2)

